{"tid":1300871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅海前悠然共你 遙望那六月飛霜","createTime":"2019-07-09T13:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T13:18:07.000Z","uid":49475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"46cb6af4b0ae72c480ad37ca8c4dacb30ef42d9c","tid":1300871,"uid":49475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YwE1FkF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYwE1FkF.jpg&h=37995641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n贏了氣勢 又怕輸去甚麼東西<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">路障不算甚麼東西</span> 你我要心情美麗<br />\n橫過了赤地天涯 仍能微笑發誓<br />\n<br />\n天祐我們 <span style=\"color: red;\">全為我們還算鬥士</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">能在最壞時刻起義</span><br />\n就算我不是先知 都有信心<br />\n天祐我們 <span style=\"color: red;\">全賴背後還有勇字</span><br />\n誰亦會是誰的天使<br />\n自愛者都是摩西 <span style=\"color: red;\">只要夠堅持</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實只係咁啱聽到呢首歌,覺得同以前聽嘅感覺好唔同,所以想分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}